direction: right
gate: Stage 1\nPass / Fail gate {
  style.stroke-dash: 4
}
graded: Stage 2\nGraded 3 / 4 / 5
A: A. Architecture & design
B: B. Systems & CPS loop
C: C. Autonomy & data
D: D. Critical evaluation
oral: Individual oral\n(gate, not modifier) {
  shape: person
}

gate -> graded: all requirements met
graded -> A
graded -> B
graded -> C
graded -> D
graded -> oral: validated per student
